! Remove header ads
www.youtube.com###masthead-ad

! Remove ads in grid list
www.youtube.com##ytd-rich-item-renderer.ytd-rich-grid-renderer:has(ytd-ad-slot-renderer.ytd-rich-item-renderer)

! Remove ads in vertical list
www.youtube.com##ytd-ad-slot-renderer.ytd-item-section-renderer

! Remove ads on video player page
www.youtube.com###player-ads